---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - BuildPrivacyPolicy" description="Privacy policy for BuildPrivacyPolicy.com. Learn what data we collect, how we use it, and how to request deletion. No ads, no tracking, no analytics.">

<div class="sticky-header">
  <div class="header-left">
    <a href="/" class="logo-link">
      <svg class="logo-icon" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 128 128" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="128" height="128" rx="28" fill="#1E3A5F"/><path d="M64 24C64 24 40 34 32 38V62C32 82 46 98 64 104C82 98 96 82 96 62V38C88 34 64 24 64 24Z" fill="#2E5A8F" stroke="#5B9BD5" stroke-width="2.5"/><path d="M52 64L60 72L78 54" stroke="white" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      <span class="logo-text">BuildPrivacyPolicy</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="page-container">
  <div class="page-card">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: July 2026</p>

    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>BuildPrivacyPolicy is a free privacy policy generator operated by <strong>HorizonTD</strong>. Our website is <a href="https://buildprivacypolicy.com">buildprivacypolicy.com</a>.</p>
    <p>Contact: <a href="mailto:ozandikbas@gmail.com">ozandikbas@gmail.com</a></p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect only the information you voluntarily enter into the privacy policy generator form. This includes your app name, developer name, contact email, and the answers you provide about your app's data practices.</p>
    <p>We do <strong>not</strong> collect personal data beyond what you enter in the form. We do not use analytics, tracking pixels, or advertising scripts.</p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>The form answers you submit are used solely to generate your privacy policy. We store this data on our servers to provide the hosted policy URL service, allowing you to link to your generated policy.</p>

    <h2>Bot Protection</h2>
    <p>We use <strong>Cloudflare Turnstile</strong> for bot protection. This service may set cookies on your device to verify that you are a human user. Cloudflare's privacy policy applies to data processed by Turnstile.</p>

    <h2>Hosting</h2>
    <p>Our website is hosted on <strong>Cloudflare Pages</strong>. Cloudflare may process certain technical data (such as IP addresses) as part of delivering our website. Cloudflare's privacy policy applies to this processing.</p>

    <h2>No Ads, No Tracking, No Analytics</h2>
    <p>We do not display advertisements. We do not use any analytics or tracking tools. We do not sell, share, or trade your data with any third parties.</p>

    <h2>Data Deletion</h2>
    <p>If you would like us to delete your stored policy data, please contact us at <a href="mailto:ozandikbas@gmail.com">ozandikbas@gmail.com</a> with your policy ID or the details you used to generate it. We will delete your data promptly.</p>

    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <p>Your form answers and generated policies are stored on our servers. We retain this data to provide the hosted policy URL service. Data is stored securely and accessed only for the purpose of serving your policy.</p>

    <h2>Not Legal Advice</h2>
    <p>BuildPrivacyPolicy is a tool that generates privacy policies based on your answers. It is <strong>not legal advice</strong> and should not be treated as a substitute for consulting a qualified legal professional.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:ozandikbas@gmail.com">ozandikbas@gmail.com</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>

</Layout>

<style>
  .sticky-header {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: white;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
    padding: 14px 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .header-left {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .logo-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .logo-link:hover {
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .logo-icon {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .logo-text {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111827;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
  }
  .page-container {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 32px 16px 80px;
  }
  .page-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 40px 36px;
    border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
  }
  .page-card h1 {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111827;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .last-updated {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #9CA3AF;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .page-card h2 {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111827;
    margin-top: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .page-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #374151;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .page-card a {
    color: #2563EB;
  }
  .page-card strong {
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
